@@TJvTipOfDay.TipFont
Summary
  \Controls the attributes of the text that displays the tip in the Tip of the Day dialog.
Description
  Set Font to specify the font to use for displaying the tips. The value of Font is a TFont object.
  Set the properties of the TFont object to specify the font face, color, size, style, and any other
