@@TJvTipOfDay.Options
Summary
  Specifies options for the dialog.
Description
  Use the Options property to customize the functionality of the dialog. Use these flags to specify
  whether the dialog:
  
  * Should be shown at startup.
  * Should use a storage component to store and retrieve the value of the "Show \Tips on StartUp"  
  checkbox.
  * Should be shown not before the parent form of the TJvTipOfDay component is shown.
See Also
  Execute

