@@TJvTipOfDay.AppStorage
Summary
  \Storage component to store the values of the Show On Startup Checkbox.
Description
  Use the AppStorage property to link the Tip of the Day component to a storage component. This
  storage component will be used to store the value of the checkbox permanently.
  
  If you don't link the component to a storage component, you have to store and retrieve the checkbox
  value manually by using OnCanShow and an OnAfterExecute event handlers. Note \Include
  toUseAppStorage in Options otherwise the storage component is <I>not</I> used.
See Also
  TJvAppStorage, TJvTipOfDay.AppStoragePath, TJvTipOfDayOption.toUseAppStorage

